<content title="Calvary Continuum Tape Catalog - Order Form">
	<heading>Calvary Continuum Tape Order and Tape Subscription Order Forms</heading>
	<p>Please be aware of the terms when ordering any audio tape from the Calvary Continuum tape catalog.</p>
	<heading>Pricing</heading>
	<p>All audio tapes are $5 each; shipping, handling and tax are included. Please enclose a check or money order made payable in US dollars, drawn on a US bank, to Calvary Chapel Austin. </p>
	<heading>Tape Subscriptions</heading>
	<p>As a tape subscriber, you will receive a tape each week of the service to which you subscribe. You may subscribe to any or all of the services at Calvary Chapel of Austin. The cost is $39 per quarter payable in advance for each service to which you subscribe (shipping, handling and tax are included in the price of the subscription). You may also sponsor a subscription to be shipped to someone else. Please enclose a check or money order made payable in US dollars drawn on a US bank to Calvary Chapel Austin.</p>
